come with USB-C connector?

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:56.000
Who is going to answer? Tim or Jony?

00:02:56.500 --> 00:02:59.750
Or will I have to wait till September, 2015.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:02.500
Steve Jobs must have been rolling in his grave.

00:03:04.750 --> 00:03:07.500
